  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>FX Swap Rate</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"abstract\" content=\"This card displays the development of FX swap rates over a term (in days).\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"This card displays the development of FX swap rates over a term (in days).\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loioa6edd42a8b85451285a58a3cd8743be1\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">FX Swap Rate</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This card displays the development of FX swap rates over a term (in days).</p>\n<p class=\"p\">With this card, you can see the development of FX swap rates over a specific term starting from\nthe key date. By default, 540 days are displayed as the term for the FX swap rates. You\ncan display more values by dragging the card.</p>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
